<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reality-n">reality <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ri'æləti/    美 /ri'æləti/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>真实；现实；事实：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>reality show</strong>
真人秀节目</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is not imagination, but reality. 
这不是想象，而是现实。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She refuses to <strong>face reality</strong>.
她不肯面对现实。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will time travel ever <strong>become a reality</strong>?
时光旅行真的会变成现实吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-reality">in reality</h3>
<p>1.<strong>实际上；事实上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Outwardly she seemed confident but in reality she felt extremely nervous. 
表面上她似乎很自信，其实她感到极其紧张。</p></div></div>